Texts.Eng: A nasty pirate named ^orange;Wrexor Nar^reset; has been harassing outer-rim systems of late and destabilizing new colonies. Can you please kill him to save countless lives?
Bring the ^green;Stormwarden^reset; to me at the ^orange;Science Outpost^reset;
I can rest easier now, knowing that colony ships carrying human survivors will no longer be attacked by that madman!
